name: Time, dedication, and darn good eats.

If breakfast is the most important meal of the day, then brunch is the most important meal of the week. We treat it with the pomp and ceremony it deserves, using farm- fresh ingredients to craft food you’ll spend the next six days dreaming about.
Buttermilk Flapjacks $16 Two flapjacks served with molasses and our signature sassafras-infused whipped cream.
Buckwheat Cakes Honey $17 Two thick buckwheat cakes served with honey and our signature sassafras-infused whipped cream.
Grits & Strawberries $16 Corn grits and local beans known as Arizona Strawberries. Served with onion, garlic,poblano, and ham gravy.
Hotcakes & Sausage $12 Cornmeal and molasses hotcakes served with sweet fennel pork sausage.
